    <example xml:id="ex_vvflimit4">
      <title>Derivatives of vector<ndash />valued functions</title>
      <statement>
        <p>Let <m>\vec r(t) = \la \cos(t) , \sin(t) , t\ra</m>. Compute <m>\vrp(t)</m> and <m>\vrp(\pi/2)</m>. Sketch <m>\vrp(\pi/2)</m> with its initial point at the origin and at <m>\vec r(\pi/2)</m>.</p>
