        <p>At <m>t=0</m>, we have <m>\vrp(0) = \la 0,0\ra=\vec 0</m>! This implies that the tangent line <q>has no direction.</q> We cannot apply <xref ref="def_vector_tangent">Definition</xref>, hence cannot find the equation of the tangent line.</p>
